Package: rustdesk-hbbs
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: systemd
Description: RustDesk ID/Rendezvous Server (HBBS)
 RustDesk HBBS is the ID/Rendezvous server component of RustDesk,
 a remote desktop software. It handles:
 - User registration and authentication
 - Connection establishment between RustDesk clients
 - NAT traversal assistance
 .
 This package provides a statically linked binary that runs on port 21116
 by default and includes a systemd service for easy deployment.